by Aikoland » Tue Apr 19, 2022 8:01 am

A classic bad RPer from a few years ago was Crazybloxian Empire. I think they're technically still around in the sense of 'they keep their nation alive' but they literally haven't posted on the forums since 2018.

But anyways, Crazybloxian Empire's whole thing was they'd declare war on/threaten to nuke basically any nation that refused to play with them, with healthy doses of godmodding and, you know, trying to involve people in RPs that they didn't consent to. It even happened to me when I rejected their application in my Gandoor Broadcasting Corporation storefront on Gandoor. They seriously responded to the rejection by saying that they were launching nukes at the Gandoor Broadcasting Corporation and were going to nuke Gandoor's capital immediately. Then when I called them out for that, they threatened to assassinate my nation's president if I didn't shut up.

As you might of figured out, they would also get mad whenever people called them out for trying to involve them in war RPs without their permission or just critiqued and criticized their poor RPing in general. I distinctly remember a mod telling them something along the lines of 'You want to make a closed news thread just for your nation? That's fine, but you don't get to complain when you try and involve other nations in your roleplaying and they don't want to be involved'

Also they had this weird obsession with some polar bear that died at a zoo in Singapore and honestly I'm only mentioning this because their first thread about the polar bear's death is kind of stupidly hilarious.
